<BaseLayout title="About VisaPathway — Multi-Passport Visa Checker" description="How VisaPathway works, our data sources, and our commitment to accuracy.">
  <h1>About VisaPathway</h1>
  <section style="max-width: 750px;">
    <p>VisaPathway is a free visa requirements checker designed for travelers with <strong>multiple passports and residence permits</strong>. Unlike other visa tools that only check one passport at a time, VisaPathway evaluates all your travel documents and recommends the best one for each destination.</p>

    <h2>Data Sources</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Passport visa matrix:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/ilyankou/passport-index-dataset">Passport Index Dataset</a> (open source, community-maintained)</li>
      <li><strong>Residence permit exemptions:</strong> Manually compiled from official government immigration websites. Every entry includes a source link.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Accuracy Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>While we strive to keep information accurate and up-to-date, <strong>visa requirements can change without notice</strong>. This tool provides general guidance only. Always verify requirements with the relevant embassy or consulate before making travel plans. We shall not be held liable for any loss or damage arising from the use of this information.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Found an error? Have a suggestion? Reach us at <strong>contact@techtools365.com</strong>.</p>
    <p>VisaPathway is a product of <a href="https://techtools365.com">TechTools365</a>.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
